Epsilon’s mission to deliver *1 View, 1 Vision, 1 Voice* and its emphasis on *collaboration*, *growth*, and *innovation* are compelling to me. I value environments where teams *work together to win together*, respect all voices, and move quickly with accountability. I would welcome the opportunity to bring my experience in *distributed systems*, *cloud platforms*, and production support to a team building data and technology products at scale.

Sincerely,
Osaid Khan
